 14th May 1917 . Got up at 8 for breakfast . Went down to trench at 1 and stay at OP all afternoon till late . Got back to batteri had some tea . 15th May 1917 . Went on shift at 5 till 8 this morn . After breakfast wrote letter for mail . Medic inspect at 2.30 . On duti 11 2 5 till 8. 16th May 1917 . Went down to the OP at 8 oclock and came back at 9 oclock . Shift quarter today to trench on work . Hope I do not stay here long . Went on duti at 10 till 2 tonight . 17th May 1917 . Got up at 8 for breakfast . Went on at 10 till 2. Day wet windi . Veri quiet . 18th May 1917 . Went on at 4 till 8 this morn . Walk up to batteri and had dinner in Fleurbaix . Came back went on duti at 4 till 6 . Did the 12 till 4 shift . 19th May 1917 . Got up at 8 for breakfast . Went on duti at 12 till 4 . Rather quiet today . Went on again at 8 till 12 . 20th May 1917 . Woke at 8 went on duti . Reliev by Tommi at 12 oclock . Left the trench at 12 30 walk up to Fleurbaix for dinner . Had a sleep all the afternoon in the shade near our old posit . Left Fleurbaix at 11 30 by hors and got to wagon line at 2 oclock tire . 21st May 1917 . Woke at 8 oclock and had breakfast . On parad at 9 oclock . Fool about all day on har . Knock off at 5 . Batteri left for posit at Plug Street tonight .
